<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>KDT 커뮤니티</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <style>
        .hero-section{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#667eea 0%,#764ba2 100%);color:#fff;padding:100px 0;}
        .card{border:none;border-radius:15px;box-shadow:0 0.125rem 0.25rem rgba(0,0,0,.075);transition:transform .3s;}
        .card:hover{transform:translateY(-5px);}
        .navbar{background:rgba(255,255,255,.95);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light fixed-top">
    <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="/"><i class="fas fa-dumbbell me-2"></i>KDT 커뮤니티</a>
        <div class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
            <a class="nav-link" href="/login"><i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt me-1"></i>로그인</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero-section">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-4">KDT 커뮤니티에 오신 것을 환영합니다</h1>
        <p class="lead mb-4">운동과 건강에 대한 정보를 공유하고 소통하는 공간입니다.</p>
        <div class="d-flex gap-3 justify-content-center">
            <a href="/admin" class="btn btn-light btn-lg"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt me-2"></i>관리자 페이지로 이동</a>
            <a href="/match/list" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg"><i class="fas fa-futbol me-2"></i>매치 보기</a>
            <a href="/match/stats" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg"><i class="fas fa-chart-bar me-2"></i>매치 통계</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row mb-4">
            <div class="col-12">
                <h2 class="text-center mb-4"><i class="fas fa-file-alt me-2"></i>최근 게시글</h2>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            {{^posts}}
                <div class="col-12">
                    <div class="text-center py-5">
                        <i class="fas fa-inbox fa-3x text-muted mb-3"></i>
                        <h4 class="text-muted">등록된 게시글이 없습니다.</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted">첫 번째 게시글을 작성해보세요!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            {{/posts}}

            {{#posts}}
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">{{title}}</h5>
                            <p class="card-text text-muted">{{contentPreview}}</p>
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                                <small class="text-muted"><i class="fas fa-user me-1"></i><span>{{authorUsername}}</span></small>
                                <small class="text-muted"><i class="fas fa-calendar me-1"></i><span>{{createdAtFmtDate}}</span></small>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-footer bg-transparent">
                            <a href="/admin" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm"><i class="fas fa-eye me-1"></i>자세히 보기</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            {{/posts}}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<footer class="bg-dark text-light py-4">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <p class="mb-0"><i class="fas fa-heart text-danger me-1"></i>KDT 커뮤니티 - 건강한 삶을 위한 공간</p>
    </div>
</footer>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
